{"tid":997941,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"危險的兔子墊材！注意！🐰","createTime":"2019-01-27T14:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T03:16:29.000Z","uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"77668862415ae775e1a83f89fdef230e397622b7","tid":997941,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"不要買松木及紅杉木的木屑(Pine &amp; Cedar Shavings)，因為有種化學物質叫酚(Aromatic Phenols)會傷兔子的肝和呼吸系統。其他墊材就沒問題，買的時候<strong>最好看清楚英文名字 !</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為依然有很多寵物店售賣這類型的墊材。<br />\n<br />\n總括來說，<strong>以下的墊材是對兔子<ins>有害</ins>：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. Pine and cedar shavings<br />\n2. Clay/Clumping litter<br />\n3. Corn cob litter<br />\n4. Scented litter<br />\n5. Newspaper / Shredded paper<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下是對兔子<ins>安全</ins>的：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. Paper pulp, 即是Carefresh (但貴！)<br />\n2. Compressed newspaper<br />\n3. Compressed sawdust pellets, 即是 Feline Pine, Wood stove pellets, Horse stall pellets (吸收力強，所以推介!)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊來源</span>: <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/care/shavings.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fcare%2Fshavings.html&d=pVnPKVlrfckw%2FdlZmyAw9%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=9e8aa0e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/care/shavings.html</a>"},{"pid":"37379e4f78937a8d4a752a873a900500d40d5849","tid":997941,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46cb7591f98b0c903ffb382c6a9ccb56fc1b4ce","tid":997941,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子奮身救貓貓！😺🐰</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n當兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。兔子正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。牠們只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y-0xUyL8V5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy-0xUyL8V5s&d=pVnPKVlrfckw%2FdlZmyAw9%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=977efdd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y-0xUyL8V5s</a>"}]}